omponent**: `frontend`\n   - **Reason**: `context deadline exceeded` 表示 `frontend` 服务在试图获取广告数据时遇到了超时问题，这通常意味着请求阻塞或者下游服务响应延迟。\n   - **Evidence**: 多个日志显示 `\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"`, 出现频率极高，达数百次。\n\n2. **Adservice 服务故障**\n   - **Component**: `adservice`\n   - **Reason**: Multiple load attempts of Byteman agent, 其中 `adservice` 服务在运行中尝试多次加载 Byteman agent，导致异常报错 `java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`.\n   - **Evidence**: 日志如 `Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`, `Agent failed to start!` 等异常。\n\n### 可能根因\n- **服务调用超时**: Frontend尝试从AdService获取广告时，AdService可能由于内部异常或响应延迟未能及时响应，这可能是导致Frontend超时的原因。\n- **AdService配置或运行时错误**: AdService中的重复加载Byteman agent问题、Agent启动失败等可能影响到服务的性能和可用性。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"java.lang.Exception\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"context deadline exceeded\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\\\" (出现次数:数百)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\",\n      \"evidence\": \"java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
